haskell-filepath (1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release:
    - There are no longer Version_0_10 interfaces - the interface is now
      stable, please use System.FilePath.
    - The library is now "filepath", not "FilePath"
  * Upstream did not release a tarball so this tarball is created from
    the darcs archive with darcs dist. The latest patch is included in the
    archive was from "Wed Apr 11 02:49:58 CEST 2007"
  * Add XS-Vcs-Browser field.

 -- Arjan Oosting <arjan@debian.org>  Fri, 13 Apr 2007 00:15:58 +0200

